        %h2.mb-2 About Our Project
        %p.lead
          As digital distribution platforms have risen in popularity, board game classics are 
          surprisingly still relevant in today’s society. However, they have failed to adapt to the technological advances of
          today’s market. This points to an opportunity for us to adapt the classics that have stood the test of time with
          some technology of our own. In our project we implement a technilogical medium to the
          classic game of Battleship. Acoustic Battleship innovates on the traditional Battleship game with acoustic
          localization technology, making accuracy part of the fun of the game.

